ActCanada Pension Plan
Old Age Security Act
SubjectTerms and Conditions of the Agreement on Social Security between Canada and the Republic of Serbia
PrecisOrder approving the TERMS AND CONDITIONS of the AGREEMENT ON SOCIAL SECURITY between the Government of Canada and the REPUBLIC OF SERBIA. The purpose of the Agreement is to coordinate the operation of Canada’s Old Age Security program and the Canada Pension Plan with the comparable pension programs of Serbia.
